                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d222">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States.</hi>
                            <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">San José</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-04-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 27, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Nicaraguan minister for foreign affairs informs me that the Nicaraguan
                    Government notified British admiral that it can not accept ultimatum of
                    England.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Baker.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
